      "message": "Also makes it work with the editor tests\n\nVersions:\n* rive runtime 3a5b5058aca009b823154ed7f92c11d599c00ae3",
      "min_defold_version": "1.12.3",
      "published_at": "2026-04-09T13:52:58Z",
